  m_text: It is the year 2100. The world's greatest minds could not foresee it, but
    the Earth is beginning to fall into ruin as a terrible calamity approaches. The
    harmful pollution us humans have been releasing into the environment has begun
    to inexplicably grow and spread out of control. Pestilence and decay has been
    destroying more and more of nature, and the government has just tasked agents
    such as myself to look for a solution in a last-ditch effort.
