  m_text: Strangely enough, while most life forms have been suffering due to the
    calamity, there is one kind of organism that has been seen in much larger sizes
    and population than ever before. This organism is called a slime mold. This yellow,
    slime-like creature has been seen practically everywhere. They feed on decaying
    organic matter, which there has been an abundance of due to the calamity, and
    they are known to thrive in moist environments...
