  m_text: I was given a mission to investigate this region, in search of a natural
    plant that is immune to the calamity through a hypothesized rare genetic variation.
    It's a long shot, but if I can find one, scientists back at the city may be able
    to cultivate it and reproduce it, to plant them back in the wild and restore
    the environment.
